citation: Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order (No. 2) 2011 (Rescinded) (Tas)
text:
Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order (No. 2) 2011 (Rescinded)

This Statutory Rule has been rescinded.

1. (Rescinded)
    The Inland Fisheries (Seasons and Waters) Amendment Order (No. 2) 2011 have been rescinded by Schedule 3 to the Redundant Legislation Repeal Act 2016
